		<title>Mayo Clinic Q&amp;#038;A: Why is fiber good for your overall health?</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-why-is-fiber-good-for-your-overall-health/</link>
		
